posts.title: Higher order functions in Javascript
posts.custom_excerpt: What makes JavaScript suitable for functional programming is that it accepts Higher-Order Functions. Higher-Order Functions are extensively used in JavaScript. If you have been programming in JavaScript for a while, you may have already used them without even knowing.
